name: Ratatoot
description: The Story of Ratatoot Ratatoot is a washed-up degen rat who YOLO’d his entire bag aping into animal coins and rug-pulling politicians. Now he’s broke af, living in a cardboard box, but planning his comeback with his own meme token. Will he moon or stay rekt in the rat race forever? This is a meme and fun project that we believe many can relate to, and we want to build a welcoming community where everyone can share jokes, enjoy memes, and laugh together.
